transcript:

Executive: Hello. Haan ji Harsh ji Saloni baat kar rahi hu Indiamart se good afternoon.

Executive: Haan. Okay. Main isme aap mujhe apni mail id bataiye to main aapko share kar deti hu google meet ka link usi pe discussion.
Customer: Aapke pass koi email id hogi hamara.
Executive: Maine aapko isliye bataya tha ki hamare pass aapka na hi number na hi koi bhi data reflect hota hai even aapki mail id aur contact number bhi nahi hota hai.
Customer: G S E
Executive: Wait a second G S E
Customer: G S E hai E for elephant.
Executive: G S E N N bataya aapne?
Customer: Nahi mam G S E fir dobara E N T E R.
Executive: Okay E N T E R
Customer: T R I S E
Executive: T R I S E
Customer: 2016
Executive: 2016
Customer: @yahoo.com
Executive: @yahoo.com. Okay ek minute call hold karega. Main aapko link share kar rahi hu.

Executive: Maine aapko link share kiya inbox mein aapke check kariye.
Customer: Nahi aaya.
Executive: Refresh karega ek dobara bhi aa jayega.

Customer: Nahi aaya hai.
Executive: Okay ek minute main aapko whatsapp pe bhejti hu.
Customer: Spam mein bhi check kar liya.
Executive: Maine aapko whatsapp pe alag se share kar diya link.
Customer: Login karte hai fir baat karte hai.
